snippet.title: Toziuha Night - Dracula's Revenge [Release Trailer] Available on Steam, Itch.io and Google Playstore
snippet.description:
Toziuha Night: Dracula's Revenge is a 2D Platform and Action Classicvania. Developed by a single person (Danny Garay).

You can buy it on Steam + Soundtrack
https://dannygaray60.itch.io/toziuha-night-order-of-the-alchemists

Purchase link at itch.io + Free Demo
https://dannygaray60.itch.io/toziuha-night-draculas-revenge

Purchase link on playstore
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.danny_garay.toziuha_night_dr

For news & updates follow me on facebook and twitter
https://www.facebook.com/toziuhanight
https://twitter.com/dannygaray60

Donations are welcome! Support me on kofi!
https://ko-fi.com/dannygaray60
